comment: Aminu (POR) commits a take foul on Howard (HOU). Since the foul occurs away from the ball under the two minute mark, Houston is awarded one free throw that can be attempted by any player on the court and they retain possession.
Howard (HOU) and Plumlee (POR) briefly engage and separate away from the play.
Howard (HOU) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Lillard (POR) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) body and affects his RSBQ.
Harden (HOU) extends his arm into McCollum (POR) and affects his ability to defend and retrieve the loose ball.
Leonard (POR) sets the screen on Ariza (HOU) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Howard (HOU) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
RHH shows that Harden (HOU) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) waist that affects his RSBQ.
Crabbe (POR) makes contact with Brewer's (HOU) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
RHH shows that Harden (HOU) cleanly strips the ball from McCollum (POR).
Lillard (POR) makes contact with Harden (HOU) that affects his RSBQ and causes him to lose control of the ball.
Terry (HOU) cleanly blocks Roberts' (POR) jump shot attempt.
Leonard (POR) makes contact with Terry's (HOU) body on his driving shot attempt.
